name: Space Travel (gulbudakk)
description:
A game I made for GitHub GameOff event. Still buggy, I didn't have time to fix it. Even the game jam lasted for a month I worked on this by myself and I had a lot of coursework to do. So it is a bit sketchy. It is one of my first games. I hope you will have fun trying to jump to the moon and the earth back and forth!

GitHub Repository: https://github.com/gulbudakk/SpaceTravelGame
